column5: Just woke up to a nice red sky.    Take care boys!!!
You tryin to scare us all on a Friday Joey?!?!?   Supposed to be a beautiful day. Have a good one Y'all.
The bay here was calm at 5AM. Was think,n of call,n in,,,cough cough.
Have the day off. Gonna see if we can get a few Smallies to dance with us this afternoon.Good luck if you get out there B
